"""Manual integration tester for the sync `Instant` client.

Mirrors the shape of `main.py` (the async sandbox) for the subset of the
surface exposed on the sync client

Run via:
    uv run --env-file .env python -m src.main_sync

Uncomment a tester call inside `main()` to exercise that surface against a
real server.
"""

